title: IAA Tonight | Deion Sanders Criticizes Hall of Fame Credentials
description: Pro Football Hall of Famer and Jackson State University Head Football Coach Deion Sanders said the quality for the Hall of Fame has been reduced. Is Prime correct in his assessment of what the Hall of Fame has become? Plus, we continue our Countdown to Kickdown to Kickoff with the Los Angeles Chargers. Will Justin Herbert make the leapto superstardom?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Ashley Nicole Moss, Omar Kelly, Brandon Flowers)
